img(width="450" alt="screenshot" height="450" src=cdn("#{site.base_url}/images/design/iot/as7screenshot.png"))
p
  | Of course one of the highest visibility examples of running JBoss projects on embedded devices (prior even to the release of the Raspberry Pi), was during the
  a[href="https://www.jboss.org/jbw2011keynote"]
    | JBossWorld 2011 keynote
  | demonstration. Here we ported Infinispan to run on a
  a[href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GuruPlug"]
    | cluster of GuruPlug
  | devices.
p
